 The dialogs contained a list of installed files, which are actually on my system.
 
 So I concluded that the files were successfully downloaded unpacked and moved to (what seems) the
 correct directory.
 
 I think I found the cause of the unexpected behavior; after restarting drscheme the documentation could be found.
 So maybe the builtin webserver should be restarted after installation of documentation?
 Alternatively a message could be presented to the user, stating that drscheme needs to be restarted.
 
 with best regards,
   Sven 
 

